flowchart LR
    A["DataFrame / SQL"] --> B["Unresolved<br/>Logical Plan"]
    B -->|analyzer<br/>(catalog lookup,<br/>type check)| C["Resolved<br/>Logical Plan"]
    C -->|optimizer rules<br/>(pushdown, pruning,<br/>constant folding)| D["Optimized<br/>Logical Plan"]
    D -->|strategies| E["Physical Plan<br/>candidates"]
    E -->|cost model| F["Selected<br/>Physical Plan"]
    F --> G["RDDs / Tasks"]
    G -->|execution| H["Results"]
    H -.->|runtime stats| F
    F -.->|AQE rewrite| D
